This pattern should be if you service is available in multiple languages.

## How to use this pattern

Language selection is achieved by rendering a language selector component in the header element, and a list of available lanauges in the footer. The header lanauge selector is for viewports larger than mobile, and the footer language selector is for viewports smaller than tablet.

If there are 3 or less available languages, the header language picker will render two links, otherwise a dropdown menu will be renedered.

